We generate a significant portion of our net revenue from gaming-related products. As a result, any decline or slowdown in the growth of the gaming industry or the declining popularity of the gaming industry could materially and adversely affect our business.
We have no specific plans to attract gamers who use only mobile devices or tablets and we have no plans to develop products specifically designed for gamers who use mobile devices or tablets. As a result, if gamers migrate to mobile devices or tablets and
